T1  - Optimal payout ratio under uncertainty and the flexibility hypothesis: Theory and empirical evidence
AU  - Lee, Cheng-Few
AU  - Gupta, Manak C.
AU  - Chen, Hong-Yi
AU  - Lee, Alice C.
